{"tid":970521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國出言恫嚇 美國會議員(Twitter)聲援台灣","createTime":"2019-01-06T01:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T09:00:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6313b0c2b13227f872bab966612a18d694019e41","tid":970521,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:38:03.000Z","msg":"中國出言恫嚇 美國會議員聲援台灣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20190105/3157434/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20190105%2F3157434%2F&d=ew77jXDyOYNVIOodbIO3mMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=23dc8b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20190105/3157434/</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者江今葉華盛頓4日專電）<span style=\"color: red;\">中國國家主席習近平日前提出對台5項原則，宣稱不放棄武力犯台，引來多位美國國會議員聲援台灣，呼籲中國停止對台威脅，美國國會對台支持堅定不移。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n美國聯邦參議員甘迺迪（John Kennedy）轉貼路透社報導透過推特表示，中國以武力威脅台灣是應受譴責且適得其反的惡劣外交手法。中國對台灣的挑釁作為危害區域穩定，也顯露中國對全球民主國家的不尊重。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦眾議員迪林肯（Lincoln Diaz-Balart）則一連推文兩則表示，對於中國以武力威脅美國民主盟邦中華民國台灣感到不齒，共產獨裁政權以脅迫、恐嚇與暴力維持政權。中國人民受其政權壓迫太久，中國必須停止威脅享有自由的台灣人民。<br />\n<br />\n多次公開為台發聲的眾議員約霍（Ted Yoho）也推文表示，習近平對台灣的威脅言論彰顯中共加強對台灣民主的邊緣化。台灣合法性不證自明，美國國會仍將堅定不移地支持台灣。<br />\n<br />\n眾議員貝肯（Don Bacon）也推文表示，台灣人民享有民主與人權，在中國死守共產主義並打壓宗教、言論、新聞自由之際，美國必須堅守對台灣長久以來的承諾，確保台灣不致遭受孤立。<br />\n<br />\n出身愛阿華州的眾議員金恩（Steve King）透過臉書表示，台灣是獨立國家，是美國與愛阿華州的民主盟邦與重要貿易夥伴，全球熱愛自由的人應譴責中國對台灣的武力恫嚇與威脅。<br />\n<br />\n眾議員葛夫曼（Glenn Grothman）、畢格斯（AndyBiggs）、龔薩雷茲（Vicente Gonzalez）與戈薩（Paul Gosar）也都推文聲援台灣。<span style=\"color: red;\">對於美國國會不分黨派力挺台灣的自由民主制度與主權，駐美國台北經濟文化代表處表示感謝。</span>（編輯：陳永昌）1080105"},{"pid":"6318b998cb67555ea8aca8a65949f05b3549acfa","tid":970521,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"習種想轉移視線點知仲辣多啲火頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f354e8d2bc65cbc067f11b6d45a14ec6cad14cf","tid":970521,"uid":59695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:52:12.000Z","msg":"雜種平仲衰過小學雞"},{"pid":"216b34f02c5d4d5ba5f4b348d5763ef5ab063a22","tid":970521,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:54:28.000Z","msg":"甘迺迪翻生撐台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597b0947fd61790342e52ca7b54e86ce94d9f333","tid":970521,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b261b351db97c5f7749ee16a61ec4a65b7684656","tid":970521,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"216b34f02c5d4d5ba5f4b348d5763ef5ab063a22","tid":970521,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:54:28.000Z","msg":"甘迺迪翻生撐台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"大把人姓甘迺迪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔係甘乃威"},{"pid":"7d6b17fcb9f8f7a38d9a856e30bbd5ff154f2de4","tid":970521,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7faec4bd07441d5e6c10e89cc139d593439afd","tid":970521,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"完全俾美國全方位屌柒，只可以靠youtube啲飛機文拎返啲自專心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0604d030bb1e96671c22505640f2aabe98a95db5","tid":970521,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6c2f11ec3ee40108673773e9bfd3c5aad86e26","tid":970521,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"<